data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to Shell Cove Community! Come home to peaceful suburbia living in this magnificent 4 bedroom 2 baths, 2 year old, 1935 sq.ft home. Situated in a wonderful location - just minutes to beautiful Tampa Bay waterfront parks, local shopping, restaurants and easy access to several Gulf Coast beaches and International Airports. From the moment you walkthrough the front door, you will see an inviting, open plan layout ideal for entertaining. The large kitchen features a center island plus full appliances including washer and dryer, and overlooks a spacious living area. The split floor plan merges form and function with the master suite consisting of an oversized bedroom connected to a roomy bathroom where you will find a walk-in shower, double vanities and walk-in closet. Enjoy undisturbed tranquility while tapping into the expansive backyard perfect for pets, entertaining or family activities with plenty of room for installing a pool. This home is move-in ready and the sellers are providing a 1-year home warranty to new owners.Call to schedule a viewing. Stop your search and start living in this incredible dream home! VA ASSUMABLE LOAN AT 3.3%, SAVE HUNDREDS EACH MONTH ON YOUR MORTGAGE PAYMENT for qualifying VA loan buyers. Creative financing for a seller financed secondary loan at below market rate may be available for the right buyer, pending lender approval.
